Class GenericNode<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • models.GenericNode<T>
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    BoardTreeNode

    public class GenericNode<T>
extends java.lang.Object
    Generic Tree Node class that represents a node of a tree. It has an attribute corresponding to a value, an attribute that corresponding to its children and an attribute corresponding to its parent.
